TestCredentialFactory.description:
CredentialFactory that reads its credentials from a plain (unencrypted) .properties file.

Secret are stored in the properties file as key/value pairs, where the key is the alias and the value is the password.

notes.value: For adequate privacy in production environments, the source file should not be readable by unauthorised users.
See the official Java Properties file format for information about escaping and special characters.
